title: Usagetimelines.Pro.1803.Apk
description:
This App displays a live graphical chart on your status bar. This chart shows and monitors how much of your Android phone / tablet CPU is being used. You can see a live display of what is excessively overloading your CPU and kill the application. You can also see which Apps run without you using them excessively and delete them if you choose. I have found Apps running without my using them and deleted them as was my preference. This App also also has a widget that simply turns the notification on and off in your status bar. 
Enjoy and re-seed please!
